OL,5, Post Office bosses secretly decided in 
OL,6, April 2014 to sack forensic accountants
OL,7, who had found bugs in their IT system, 
OL,8, documents obtained by the BBC show.    
OL,10,FThey also reveal the government had    
OL,11,Fknowledge of the decision, taken by a  
OL,12,FPost Office board sub-committee,       
OL,13,Fcodenamed "Project Sparrow".           
OL,15,FFormer sub-postmaster Alan Bates said  
OL,16,Fit was further proof of a "total       
OL,17,Fcover-up".                             
OL,19,FThe Post Office said it would be       
OL,20,Finappropriate to comment.              
